      "content": "{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"What is simply called \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"text\":\"The Gorge \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" is planar rift zone connected to the hells. It was formed long ago and little written history remains on it's origins. The inhabitants of the Four Kingdoms valiantly hold the line against the demons that clamber out from the gorge. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Demonic incursions from the gorge are sporadic and unpredictable. The demons rise in waves. Some years there's hardly an imp to be seen, other years the Four Kingdoms teeter on the brink of complete annihilation due to the sheer numbers of demons spewed it. \"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\"}]}",
